channel.title: XN - Old Skool [Dubstep]
channel.description:
Some 2011-2012 inspired dubstep (complete with "dank" misspelling of title)that i made a long time ago. Decided to finally let it see the light and reach other people's ears.
https://soundcloud.com/xn-extras/old-skool
Also on Audius
https://audius.co/m_x_c_n/old-skool-13722
Edit: Finally uploaded to YouTube.
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5NvdiqyWLP4
This marks the first track in a handful of uploads that i'll be doing throughout the next few weeks of old and new tracks. Not an album, but more of a "2019 in review" playlist.
